UADataType.Description: This enumeration defines the values of the FlcConnectionStatus of an FlcConnectionEndpointType.

Field.Name: Initial
Field.Description: Initial status of the logical connection. No communication-model objects referenced.

Field.Name: Ready
Field.Description: Logical connection is ready to operate, Communication-model objects are referenced but not enabled.

Field.Name: PreOperational
Field.Description: PreOperational status of the logical connection, Data output is active, but no input data received.

Field.Name: Operational
Field.Description: Operational status of the logical connection, Data output is active, and input data has been received.

Field.Name: Error
Field.Description: The logical connection has encountered an Error.

Field.Name: CommInitial

Field.Name: CommError

Field.Name: DeviceFailure
Field.Description: At least one of the top-level Assets has its DeviceHealth set to Failure.

Field.Name: DeviceCheckFunction
Field.Description: At least one of the top-level Assets has its DeviceHealth set to CheckFunction.

Field.Name: DeviceMaintenanceRequired
Field.Description: At least one of the top-level Assets has its DeviceHealth set to MaintenanceRequired.

Field.Name: DeviceOffSpec
Field.Description: At least one of the top-level Assets has its DeviceHealth set to OffSpec.

Field.Name: SubOperationalWarning
Field.Description: One of the SubFunctionalEntities indicates a warning.

Field.Name: SubOperationalError
Field.Description: One of the SubFunctionalEntities indicates an error.
